          "id": "aqua-4b193fd1ee73cd3d",
          "text": "A debtor reached an agreement with his creditor to repay a loan by making a monthly payment which is double of the amount she paid the previous month. If the debtors first payment was $200, and he is expected to pay back 51200, how many months will it take to fully repay the loan?",
