          "text": "The consumption of diesel per hour of a bus varies directly as square of its speed. When the bus is travelling at 60 kmph its consumption is 1 litre per hour. if each litre costs $60 and other expenses per hous is $ 60, then what would be the minimum expenditure required to cover a distance of 600 Km?",
