          "explanation": "let each side of the square be a , then area = a x a\nNew side = 125a / 100 = 5a / 4\nNew area =(5a x 5a) / (4 x 4) = (25a²/16)\nincreased area== (25a²/16) - a²\nIncrease %= [(9a²/16 ) x (1/a² ) x 100]% = 56.25%\nAnswer: B"
