          "explanation": "2:3\n2x + 10 : 3x + 10 = 3 : 4\n4[2x + 10] = 3[3x + 10]\n8x + 40 = 9x + 30\n9x - 8x = 40 - 30\nx = 10\nThen smallest number is = 2\n2x = 20\nC"
