          "explanation": "Total cars=4\n1.15*4=4.6->Service Cost\nFuel Cost in Sports Car = 2*32*0.4=25.6\nFuel Cost in Executive Car=25.6*7/4=44.8\nTotal Fuel Cost = 25.6+44.8=70.4\nCost to fuel car = 70.4+4.6=75\nAnswer: B"
