          "explanation": "Speed = [36 * 5/18] m/sec = 10 m/sec; Time = 1 min. = 60 sec.\nLet the length of the train and that of the platform be x meters.\nThen, 2x/60 = 10 => x = 10 * 60 / 2 = 300\nAnswer: B"
