          "id": "aqua-49c3a68c96fdd1c7",
          "text": "7% of the total quantity of rice is lost in grinding when a country has to import 6 million tonnes, but when only 7 3/4% is lost, it can import 3 million tonnes. Find the quantity of rice grown in the country.",
