          "correctOptionId": "opt-B",
          "explanation": "Let total number be x\nNo in the interior = (x/4)^2\nNo outside = 4\nSo : x - (x/4)^2=4\nx^2-16x+64=0\n(x-8)^2=0\nSo x=8\nB"
