          "explanation": "S.I. = (1000 * 16 * 4)/100 = Rs. 640\nC.I. = [1000 * (1 + 16/100)4 - 1000] = Rs. 810.6 Difference = (810.6-640) = Rs. 170.6\nAnswer: C"
