          "id": "aqua-f5abd6acfedbdfcc",
          "text": "A cargo ship carrying four kinds of items, doohickies, geegaws, widgets, and yamyams, arrives at the port. Each item weighs 2, 11, 5, and 7 pounds, respectively, and each item is weighed as it is unloaded. If, in the middle of the unloading process, the product of the individual weights of the unloaded items equals 104,350,400,000 pounds, how many widgets have been unloaded?",
