          "correctOptionId": "opt-B",
          "explanation": "(a) Since loga (a) = 1, so log10 (10) = 1.\n(b) log (2 + 3) = log 5 and log (2 x 3) = log 6 = log 2 + log 3\nlog (2 + 3) log (2 x 3)\n(c) Since loga (1) = 0, so log10 (1) = 0.\n(d) log (1 + 2 + 3) = log 6 = log (1 x 2 x 3) = log 1 + log 2 + log 3.\nSo, (b) is incorrect.\nAnswer is B."
