          "explanation": "Let the number of students who wrote the exam be x.\nTotal marks of students = 80 x.\nTotal marks of (x - 5) students = 92(x - 5)\n80x - (5 * 20) = 92(x - 5)\n360 = 12x => x = 30\nANSWER:C"
