          "explanation": "Let T be the total number of passengers.\nLet x be the number of people with round trip tickets.\n0.2T had round trip tickets and took their cars.\n0.2x had round trip tickets and took their cars.\n0.2x = 0.2T\nx = T\nThe answer is E."
