          "explanation": "given,FOG + FOG + FOG + FOG = 1464\n4(FOG)=1464\n=>FOG=366\nFace value of F is:3\nFace value of O is:6\nFace value of G is:6\nso F+O+G=3+6+6=15\nANSWER:E"
