          "explanation": "Straightaway use answer options ( Ignoring the decimal point ) -\n(A)  1,6\n1*5 + 6*7 => 47 ( Incorrect )\n(B)  2,7\n2*5 + 7*7 => 59 ( Incorrect )\n(C)  3,5\n3*5 + 5*7 => 50 ( Incorrect )\n(D)  4,3\n4*5 + 3*7 => 41 ( Incorrect )\n(E)  5,3\n5*5 + 3*7 => 46 ( Correct )\nHence answer will be (E)"
