          "id": "aqua-d14cd44cc1a07b8d",
          "text": "An investor purchased 100 shares of stock X at 8 1/8 dollars per share and sold them all a year later at 24 dollars per share. If the investor paid a 2 percent brokerage fee on both the total purchase price and the total selling price, which of the following is closest to the investor's percent gain on this investment?",
