          "explanation": "Let number of passengers = x, 2x, 7x\nand Rate = 5y, 4y, 2y\nNow, since income = Rate × Number of passengers\n∴ Income = 5xy, 8xy, 14xy\n∴ Income in ratio = 5 : 8 : 14\n∴ Income from A.C. sleeper class = 5/5+8+14×54,000\n= 10,000\nAnswer D"
