          "id": "aqua-76506ccc3249ec89",
          "text": "A certain auto manufacturer sold 5% fewer vehicles in 2007 than in 2006. If the manufacturer sold 3.0 million vehicles in 2006, how many vehicles, to the nearest 10,000, did the manufacturer sell in 2007?",
