          "correctOptionId": "opt-C",
          "explanation": "The runner runs the first 20 miles at speed v and the second 20 miles at speed v/2.\nThe time T2 to run the second half must be twice the time T1 to run the first half.\nT2 = 2*T1 = T1+8\nT1 = 8 and so T2 = 16.\nThe answer is C."
