          "correctOptionId": "opt-D",
          "explanation": "A+B 10days work = 10*1/40 = 1/4\nRemaining work = 1-1/4 = 3/4\n3/4 work is done by A in 12 days\nwhole work will be done by A in 12*4/3 = 16days\nAnswer is D"
