          "id": "aqua-325d3b4ae4947ab0",
          "text": "When processing flower-nectar into honey bees' extract, a considerable amount of water gets reduced. How much flower-nectar must be processed to yield 1kg of honey, if nectar contains 50% water, and the honey obtained from this nectar contains 40% water?",
