          "correctOptionId": "opt-A",
          "explanation": "Time taken to meet for the first time at the starting point\n= LCM { length of the track / speed of A , length of the track / speed of B}\n= LCM { 600/ (36 * 5/18) , 600/ (54 * 5 /18) }\n= LCM (60, 40)\n=120 sec.\nAnswer:A"
