          "correctOptionId": "opt-A",
          "explanation": "Explanation:\nTotal sale for 5 months = Rs. (6435 + 6927 + 6855 + 7230 + 6562) = Rs. 34009.\nRequired sale = Rs. [ (6500 x 6) - 34009 ]\n= Rs. (39000 - 34009)\n= Rs. 4991.\nAnswer: A"
