          "correctOptionId": "opt-A",
          "explanation": "Let the CP be Rs. x.\nHad he offered 10% discount, profit = 8%\nProfit = 8/100 x and hence his SP = x + 8/100 x\n= Rs. 1.08x = 18000 - 10/100(18000)\n= 18000 - 1800 = Rs. 16200\n=> 1.08x = 16200\n=> x = 15000\nAnswer: A"
