          "id": "aqua-2d3516e54f0acc44",
          "text": "A, B and C started a business with capitals of Rs. 8000, Rs. 10000 and Rs. 12000 respectively. At the end of the year, the profit share of B is Rs. 1800. The difference between the profit shares of A and C is?",
