          "id": "aqua-8d9f49ea9971a2dd",
          "text": "A total of $20,000 was invested in two certificates of deposit at simple annual interest rates of 6 percent and 10 percent, respectively. If the total interest on the two certificates was $1,440 at the end of one year, what fractional part of the $20.000 was invested at the higher rate?",
