          "correctOptionId": "opt-D",
          "explanation": "First persons investment = x\nSecond persons investment = x + 1000\nThird persons investments = x + 2000\nx + x + 1000 + x + 2000 = 9000\n3x = 6000\nx = 2000\nRatio = 2000 : 3000 : 4000\n2:3:4\n4/9 * 2700 = 1200\nAnswer:D"
