          "id": "aqua-7cf6c89fc6539eec",
          "text": "Jill bought items costing $3.45, $1.99, $6.59, and $12.98. She used a coupon worth $2.50.\nIf Jill had $50.00 when she went into the store, how much did she have when she left?",
