          "explanation": "16^5*15^4*14^3*13^2 = x\nUnits digit of x will be\n6^5 * 5^4 * 4^3 * 3^2\n=6 * 5 * 4 * 9\n= 1080\nTherefore , units digit of x = 0\nAnswer E"
