          "id": "aqua-4c985a4c2fc12333",
          "text": "X and Y started a business by investing Rs.36000 and Rs.42000 respectively after 4 months Z joined in the business with an investment of Rs.48000, then find share of Z in the profit of Rs.13750 ?",
