          "text": "John and David were each given X dollars in advance for each day they were expected to perform at a community festival. John eventually performed on all 30 days of the festival, while David performed on 5 fewer days than John performed. If David gives John y dollars of her advance payment so that they would have each received the same daily rate, what was John paid in advance, in terms of Y?",
