          "id": "aqua-ec7d34a903972ab0",
          "text": "The average expenditure of a labourer for 3 months was 85 and he fell into debt. In the next 4 months by reducing his monthly expenses to 60 he not only cleared off his debt but also saved 30. His monthly income is",
