          "correctOptionId": "opt-E",
          "explanation": "Income of 3 months = (3 × 85) – debt\n= 255 – debt\nIncome of the man for next 4 months\n= 4 × 60 + debt + 30\n= 270 + debt\n∴ Income of 10 months = 525\nAverage monthly income = 525 ÷ 10 = 52.5\nAnswer E"
