          "explanation": "The number of matches in first round,\n= 6C2 +6C2;\nNumber of matches in next round,\n= 6C2;\nNumber of matches in semifinals,\n= 4C2;\nTotal number of matches,\n= 6C2 +6C2+6C2+4C2+2.\n= 53.\nC"
