          "explanation": "Explanation:\nWork done by the inlet in 1 hour =\n1/6−1/8=1/24\nWork done by inlet in 1 min=1/24∗1/60=1/1440\n=>Volume of 1/1440 part = 4 liters\nVolume of whole = (1440 * 4) litres = 5760 litres.\nOption C"
