          "id": "aqua-a4a5c4894d075633",
          "text": "Rs. 6000 is lent out in two parts. One part is lent at 7% p.a simple interest and the other is lent at 8% p.a simple interest. The total interest at the end of one year was Rs. 450. Find the ratio of the amounts lent at the lower rate and higher rate of interest?",
