          "correctOptionId": "opt-A",
          "explanation": "Explanation:\nWe know that,\nTime=Distance/Speed\nSpeed=20 km/hr=20∗5/18m/sec=50/9m/sec\nTime =(400∗9/50)=72sec=1 1/5min\nOption A"
