          "explanation": "Given that there are three blue marbles, four red marbles, six green marbles and two yellow marbles. When four marbles are picked at random, then the probability that none is blue is\n= ¹²C₄/¹⁵C₄\n= (12 * 11 * 10 * 9)/(15 * 14 * 13 * 12)\n= 33/91\nAnswer: B"
