          "correctOptionId": "opt-E",
          "explanation": "x is n% of y MEANS x= (n/100 )* y------------------------eq1\nz is m% of y MEANS z= (m/100 )* y------------------------eq2\nFind equation of xz\nsubstitute value of y from 2nd equation into Ist equation\nso x= (n/100)*(100z/m)\nso x= (n/m)z\nor x= (100n/m)z/100\nso answer Q is 100n/m %.E"
