          "text": "Jordan passed a point on a track at a constant speed of 50 miles per hour. Then, 15 minutes later, Pauline passed the same point at a constant speed of 60 miles per hour. If both runners maintained their speeds , how long after he passed the gas station did Pauline catch up with Jordan?",
