          "correctOptionId": "opt-C",
          "explanation": "Here N = 18=2×32\nϕ(18)=18(1−12)(1−13) = 6\nSo 56 when divided by 18, remainder is 1.\nSo we can write the given expression 5100=(56)16×54 = (1)16×54 = 52×52=7×7=49\nNow 49 when divided by 18, remainder is 13.\nC"
