          "id": "aqua-1a57f3edc29d6458",
          "text": "There are 4 people of different heights standing in order of increasing height. The difference is 2 inches between the first person and the second person, and also between the second person and the third person. The difference between the third person and the fourth person is 6 inches and the average height is 79. How tall is the fourth person?",
