          "correctOptionId": "opt-A",
          "explanation": "Let B joined for x months. Then\n85000×12:42500×x=3:1\n⇒850×12:425x=3:1\n⇒850×12×1=3×425x\n⇒850×4=425x\n⇒x=8\nAnswer is A."
