          "correctOptionId": "opt-A",
          "explanation": "Let x be the number of men.\nNumber of matches men play among themselves is 2*(xC2)\nNumber of matches men play with women is 2*(3x)\n2*(xC2) - 2*(3x) =78\nx=13\nDifference between men and women is 13-3=10.\nANSWER A"
