          "correctOptionId": "opt-A",
          "explanation": "A\n47 km\nThe total distance covered by the car in the first 10 hours = 38 + 40 + 42 + 44 + 46 + 48 + 50 + 52 + 54 + 56= sum of 10 terms in AP whose first term is 30 and last term is 56 = 10/2 [38 + 56] = 470 km."
