          "correctOptionId": "opt-A",
          "explanation": "(0.75*0.75*0.75-0.001)=0.75^3 -0.1^3\n0.75*0.75-0.075+0.01=0.75^2-0.1^2\na^3-b^3=(a+b)(a^2-ab+b^2)\nso after cancellation remainning term is (a+b) i.e 0.75+0.1=0.85\nnearly to 0.845\nANSWER:A"
