          "id": "aqua-4c0136734b4982af",
          "text": "Of 30 applicants for a job, 11 had at least 4 years' experience, 18 had degrees, and 3 had less than 4 years' experience and did not have a degree.How many of the applicants had at least 4 years' experience and a degree?",
