          "id": "aqua-884107ba443dd5b8",
          "text": "Griffin has a bag of marbles that contains 7 black marbles and 5 red marbles. If he removes 3 marbles at random without replacing any of the marbles, what is the probability that all 3 marbles selected will be black?",
