          "correctOptionId": "opt-B",
          "explanation": "2x + 15 > 5\ni.e 2x >5-15\ni.e. 2x > -10\ni.e. x > -5\nAlso, 5x - 13 < 7\ni.e. 5x <7+13\ni.e 5x < 20\ni.e x < 4\ni.e. -5 < x < 4\nAnswer: Option B"
