          "id": "aqua-46f489c872cc8bb3",
          "text": "Bruce and Anne can clean their house in 4 hours working together at their respective constant rates. If Anne’s speed were doubled, they could clean their house in 3 hours working at their respective rates. How many Q hours does it currently take Anne to clean the house on her own?",
