          "explanation": "Explanation:\nDistance = 165 m\nRelative speed = 60+6 = 66 kmph (Since both the train and the man are in moving in opposite direction)\n= 66×10/36 mps = 110/6 mps\nTime = distance/speed = 165/(110/6) = 9 s\nAnswer: Option A"
