          "correctOptionId": "opt-A",
          "explanation": "Gain in 2 years\n= Rs.[(5000 x (25/4)\tx(2/100))-((5000 x 4 x 2)/100)]\n= Rs. (625 - 400)\n= Rs. 225.\nGain in 1 year = Rs.(225/2)\n= Rs. 112.50\nANSWER :A"
