          "correctOptionId": "opt-D",
          "explanation": "Let actual price was 100.\nAfter three successive discount this will become,\n100 ==20% discount => 80 ==10% discount => 72 ==5% discount = 68.4\nNow Compare,\n68.4 = 6600\n1 = 6600/68.4\n100 = (6600*100)/68.4 = Rs. 9649.\nAnswer: Option D"
