          "explanation": "3J + 2S = 69\n2J + 3S = 76\n----------------\n5J + 5S = 145 ----(divide by 5)---> J + S = 29\n3J + 2S = J + 2(J + S) = J + 58 = 69 ---> J = 11\n3*11 + 2S = 69\n33 + 2S = 69\n2S = 36\nS = 18\nAnswer: E"
