          "correctOptionId": "opt-B",
          "explanation": "Since s* is defined as the greatest positive even integer less than or equal to s, then 5.2* = 4 (the greatest positive even integer less than or equal to 5.2 is 4).\nHence, 5.2 – 5.2* = 5.2 - 4 = 1.2\nAnswer: B."
