          "explanation": "Right Answer Explanation:\nx : 6\ny : 100\n90\n10 : 90 – y\n(90-y)/6 = 10/x = ………..(1)\nIn the second case,\nx 4\ny 90\n84\n6 84-y\nTherefore (84-y)/4 = 6/x ………..(2)\nDividing (1) and (2)\n=\n540 – 6y = 1260 – 15y\n9y = 720\ny = 80\nx = 60/(90-80) = 60/10 = 6 kg\nQuantity of zinc in x = 80% of x\n= 0.8 6\n= 4.8 kg\nWeight and percentage of zinc is 4.8 kg or 80%\nB"
