          "correctOptionId": "opt-C",
          "explanation": "LCM of 8 = 4\n1/2 marking are (Table of 2) 0...... 2 ........... 4\n(Total = 3)\n1/4 marking are (Table of 1) 0 ....... 1 ...... 2...... 3........ 4 (Total = 5)\nOverlapping markings are 0 ........ 2 ......... 4 (Total = 3)\nTotal markings = 3+5-3 = 5\nAnswer = C"
