          "explanation": "Let the fraction be x. Then,\nx:1/27 = 3/7 : 5/9\nx × 5/9 = 1/27 × 3/7\nx × 5/9 = 1/9 × 1/7\nx × 5/9 = 1/63\nx × 5 = 9/63\n5x = 1/7 = 1/35\nB)"
