          "explanation": "1/4 CP = 210 SP = 21*(80/100) = 168\nSP = 840*(120/100) = 1008\n1008 - 168 = 840\n3/4 SP = 630\nGain = 210\n630 --- 210\n100 --- ? => 33 1/3%\nAnswer: C"
