          "correctOptionId": "opt-D",
          "explanation": "Area of the four walls = 2h(l + b)\nSince there are doors and windows, area of the walls\n= 2 * 12 (15 + 25) - (6 * 3) - 3(4 * 3)\n= 906 sq.ft.\nTotal cost = 906 * 5 = Rs. 4530\nAnswer: D"
